metadata.name: Countach Classic
metadata.description:
A Lamborghini Countach LP400 in front of Villa Erba, Como (Italy)  
Does it get any better?  
•  
Shot on Nikon D800 + Nikkor 24-70 2.8G  
PNG 16-bit  
4900x3500  
•  
While owning this NFT you can redeem (once) a signed and numbered fine art for 0.1 ETH.  
Check what else you [can/can't do](https://www.tobephoto.com/nft-license/) with the hi-res file included in this NFT.
